Date: Sat, 11 Jul 2026 15:22:01 +0300
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] Metal Mutant port integration hooks (mmx module)

Wires the self-contained mmx module (mmx.c/mmx.h/mmx_font.h, shipped
separately) into the engine:

- CMakeLists: build src/mmx.c
- main.c: metal.ini config (data dir, fullscreen, scale, mute,
  language, cheats), default data path next to the exe, reimplemented
  -u unpack mode (was stubbed out upstream)
- script.c: apply translation patching in script_init
- sys_sdl2.c: window title, OSD renderer, cheat hotkeys (F5-F8),
  Alt+Enter fullscreen toggle, per-frame cheat freeze; F9 wav export
  removed

Co-Authored-By: Claude Fable 5 <noreply@anthropic.com>
